    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Platforming Revolution</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/7d5ae9f455e0c9bd2b86c4e9d7ef16e0.poster.avif?t=1677546214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/7d5ae9f455e0c9bd2b86c4e9d7ef16e0.webm?t=1677546214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/7d5ae9f455e0c9bd2b86c4e9d7ef16e0.mp4?t=1677546214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>See everything, everywhere, all at once! With a view of the entire stage at all times, you'll never be caught off-guard and you'll always be able to get the drop on your enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A new spin on celebration</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/90f823ae2e80618e9cf78fc1919d8671.poster.avif?t=1677546214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/90f823ae2e80618e9cf78fc1919d8671.webm?t=1677546214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/90f823ae2e80618e9cf78fc1919d8671.mp4?t=1677546214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Doing finishers on your opponents is more than just a flex! It'll actually add to your score and help you win the game.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Zombots are around</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"{STEAM_APP_IMAGE}/extras/Zombots_jan_23.gif/img]\nWant to team up to see how high on the leaderboard you can get? We got you! Zombots increase in numbers and complexity to push the limits of your cooperation.\n\n[h2]Dance circles around your enemies[/h2]\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/a0df51b232de6001eb82bc7f2aee9643.poster.avif?t=1677546214\" mp4=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/a0df51b232de6001eb82bc7f2aee9643.mp4?t=1677546214\" webm=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/a0df51b232de6001eb82bc7f2aee9643.webm?t=1677546214\" width=\"600\" height=\"338\"]\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" /></span>[/imgvid]\nTaunting raises your life! Flex to better health.\n\n[h2]Customization rotation[/h2]\n[imgvid poster.avif=\"\" webm=\"\" mp4=\"<br>Want to team up to see how high on the leaderboard you can get? We got you! Zombots increase in numbers and complexity to push the limits of your cooperation.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dance circles around your enemies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/a0df51b232de6001eb82bc7f2aee9643.poster.avif?t=1677546214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/a0df51b232de6001eb82bc7f2aee9643.webm?t=1677546214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/a0df51b232de6001eb82bc7f2aee9643.mp4?t=1677546214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Taunting raises your life! Flex to better health.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customization rotation</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/ee732e414cd2476fa4aa101e3e073299.poster.avif?t=1677546214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/ee732e414cd2476fa4aa101e3e073299.webm?t=1677546214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/ee732e414cd2476fa4aa101e3e073299.mp4?t=1677546214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/9c6a306219383e2b383edd8c28dab1d7.poster.avif?t=1677546214\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/9c6a306219383e2b383edd8c28dab1d7.webm?t=1677546214\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714270/extras/9c6a306219383e2b383edd8c28dab1d7.mp4?t=1677546214\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Gain chips after each match to spend on wearables, finishers, taunts, sprints, and more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >We're out of puns</h2>But join us anyway in our orbit!",
